Finally!! Little 14 month old toddler Devyaan took his first flight ever and went on his first vacation 😬🌦✈️ He made a fabulous plan to fully enjoy the monsoons, so he took his mom and dad to Goa and gave everyone the best time ever♥️
Special mention to the wonderful staff at @itcgrandgoa for making this one extra special for Devyaan. Big love to the @vistara crew for your care♥️
We made memories to cherish forever..

Thank you for the love your shower every year on this day- Shreya Ghoshal Day ♥️♥️ Always grateful to my fans♥️ 
#SGians #TeamShreya #SGFamily

Time flies by quickly with the right person. I truly believe in these words because @shiladitya makes everything easy for me and our little family. I still wonder what I would do without you - be it beginning a life together as newlyweds or welcoming a precious little one, you have stood by my side like my ‘equal half’.

7 years, 3 lockdowns, and 1 baby later, I have appreciated your presence even more and I can happily say that Devyaan is blessed to have such an amazing father like you. More than anything else, he will be learning the norms of equal partnering and parenting from the very beginning. I know we both still have a long way to go but at this moment I feel immensely proud to have shared this beautiful journey of parenthood with you.

Thanks to this beautiful film by @PampersIndia that got me all teary-eyed, with its poignant message. It reminded me of how hands-on you were as a father since the very first day and, continue to be the same even today.

I urge everyone to watch and share this beautiful film, and pledge to spend quality time with your baby while you have the chance.

#ItTakes2 #PampersIndia #EqualParenting #AMessageFromDad #PampersPremiumCare

Planet Earth and life on it has been around for billions of years. But in just the last few decades, human beings have destroyed a fundamental aspect needed for the survival of almost all life on Earth. I am talking about the soil.

87% of life on Earth depends on soil. 95% of humanity's food comes from soil. But the United Nations says we are destroying 120,000 square kilometers of soil every year, because it is losing its richness and essentially turning into sand. This is happening in every part of the world.

We have just a few decades to turn this around. We need to Save Soil because our lives depend on soil. A good time to start is right now. Let us make it happen.

Thank you @sadhguru ji for inspiring millions of us and guiding this generation towards taking care of our Mother Earth🙏🏻

Visit savesoil.org for more information

#SaveSoil #savesoilmovement

So much love and blessings have poured in from all over the world for this little one. Here are some yum cakes created by @mahekmandlik that were sent by many of my sweet fans. Wanted to give my thanks on behalf of Devyaan. Grateful ♥️🙏🏻

Happy birthday to the first time mama😘 @soumghoshal ♥️♥️♥️ Can’t believe how time has flown. You were the first baby I held in my arms who made me fall in love so deeply with that perfect tiny human. My little brother, I am so lucky to be called your didi.. And now you are the most favourite person of your nephew #Devyaan shona. My world is so blessed and complete. My two babies are born in the same month too, just a week apart♥️♥️ 
This throwback video of Devyaan’s annaprashan makes me so emotional always. You made it against all odds to fly home to feed him his first solid food. Mama bhanje ki jodi duniya ki best jodi!! 😬😍♥️ #happybirthdaysoumyadeepghoshal 
#SoumyadeepGhoshal
